-electronic cross section\ncalculations by identifying the dominant resonance structure and features\nacross an energy range of hundreds of eV.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Feb 2015 14:53:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-24"}
